### 4. Systemic Risk (15%)

```python
# Inputs: DefiLlama API (free, no key)
# /v2/charts → sector TVL | /protocol/{slug} → protocol TVL

tvl_change_7d       = (tvl_now - tvl_7d_ago) / tvl_7d_ago
proto_tvl_change_7d = (proto_tvl_now - proto_tvl_7d_ago) / proto_tvl_7d_ago

SECTOR_FLOOR = -0.20  # -20% sector TVL = full stress
PROTO_FLOOR  = -0.15  # -15% protocol TVL = full flight

sector_score       = clamp(-tvl_change_7d / 0.20 * 100, 0, 100)
proto_flight_score = clamp(-proto_tvl_change_7d / 0.15 * 100, 0, 100)

S_systemic_risk = clamp(
  0.60 * sector_score + 0.40 * proto_flight_score,
  0, 100
)
# Note: near 0 during stable periods. Spikes during events like FTX.
# Future inputs: utilization rate, whale activity (v1.1+)
```

