## Data Sources

| Source         | What                              | Cadence        | Cost         |
| -------------- | --------------------------------- | -------------- | ------------ |
| Goldsky        | Aave V3 + Moonwell position data  | 60s + events   | Free (apply) |
| Dune Analytics | Protocol data, liquidation events | 60s + events   | Free         |
| The Graph      | Fallback for Goldsky/Dune         | On failover    | Free         |
| Chainlink      | Live asset prices (on-chain read) | 60s + triggers | Free         |
| CoinGecko      | Price history, volatility (30d)   | 60s (cached)   | Free 30/min  |
| DefiLlama      | TVL history, exploit DB           | 60s            | Free, no key |

### Goldsky + Dune Combined Strategy

- **Goldsky**: real-time position indexing via subgraph/mirror on Base
- **Dune**: fills gaps where Goldsky subgraph coverage is incomplete (esp. Moonwell)
- **Failover order**: Goldsky → Dune → The Graph
- Apply for Goldsky indie/Protocol Camp free tier before integrating

### CoinGecko Rate Limit

30 calls/min on free tier. Cache per-asset per-cycle to avoid hitting limit at 10-user scale.

