## Build Order (Week 1–2)

```
1. Implement clamp(), std_dev(), pearson_corr() → unit test with synthetic data
2. S_position_health → test with mock HF values (1.0, 1.5, 2.0+)
3. S_asset_risk → connect CoinGecko, test vol calculation
4. S_protocol_safety → load from config, verify Aave ≈11 Moonwell ≈46
5. S_systemic_risk → connect DefiLlama, verify near-zero on stable data
6. Compose S_total → run against a few real positions on Base
7. Connect Goldsky + Dune → replace mock data with live feeds
8. Wire prospective mode → Compass
9. Wire active mode → Watch + Advisor
```

